------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE AND ATTRIBUTION OF UNDERLYING SOURCES
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This CC BY 4.0 grant covers the ORIGINAL COMPILATION contributed by the authors:
the class-to-code mappings, the shape-retrieval similarity scores, the
discussion-presence flags, the constructive-identity mapping, the 279-correction
selection, the field schema, and the accompanying scripts and documentation.

The dataset records FACTUAL values (character codes, official readings, page/entry
identifiers, reproduction URLs) obtained from third-party sources. These underlying
sources retain their own rights and must also be credited by reusers:

  * Glyph images and class labels: HUST-OBC (Wang et al., Scientific Data, 2024),
    distributed under CC BY 4.0.
  * Official readings, glyph codes, and exegetical cross-references: the Yinqi
    Wenyuan platform (Key Laboratory of Oracle Information Processing, Anyang
    Normal University). Readings are reproduced as factual data via the platform's
    public, login-free API.

This deposit does NOT redistribute any copyrighted material from the underlying
works: it contains no scanned pages of the Jiaguwenzi Gulin, Leizuan, or glyph
dictionaries, and no official glyph fonts. Only codes, identifiers, factual
readings, and reproduction URLs are included, so that any user can regenerate the
evidence from the authoritative source.

Reusers intending to redistribute anything beyond these factual records (e.g.
scanned pages or fonts) must obtain permission from the respective rights holders.
